description:
The Work properties element set consists of properties representing attributes and relationships of the RDA *Work* entity.

Version: 1.0.0

P10001.label: has respondent
P10001.description: Relates a work to a person who is a candidate for a degree who defends or opposes a thesis provided by the praeses in an academic disputation.

P10002.label: has identifier for work
P10002.description: Relates a work to an appellation of work that consists of a code, number, or other string, usually independent of natural language and social naming conventions, used to identify a work.

P10003.label: has other distinguishing characteristic of work (Deprecated)
P10003.description: Relates a work to a characteristic, other than form of work, date of work, or place of origin of the work, that serves to differentiate a work from another work with the same preferred title of work. (Deprecated)

P10004.label: has category of work
P10004.description: Relates a work to a type to which a work belongs.

P10005.label: has appellee corporate body
P10005.description: Relates a work to a corporate body against whom an appeal is taken on a decision of a lower court recorded in a legal work of a higher court.

P10006.label: has degree granting institution
P10006.description: Relates a work to a corporate body who approves a work that is a thesis associated with an academic degree.

P10007.label: has hosting institution
P10007.description: Relates a work to a corporate body who hosts a conference, exhibition, or other event that gives rise to a work, but has little or no responsibility for the content.

P10008.label: has production company
P10008.description: Relates a work to a corporate body who is responsible for managing the financial, technical, and organizational aspects of a production for stage, screen, sound recording, television, webcast, etc.

P10009.label: has appellant corporate body
P10009.description: Relates a work to a corporate body who appeals a decision of a lower court recorded in a legal work of a higher court.

P10010.label: has plaintiff corporate body
P10010.description: Relates a work to a corporate body who brings a suit in a civil proceeding.

P10011.label: has court governed
P10011.description: Relates a work to a corporate body that is a court governed by court rules, regardless of their official nature.

P10012.label: has numbering of part
P10012.description: Relates a work to a designation that is assigned to a work to identify its position in a sequence of individual parts of a larger work.

P10013.label: has film director agent
P10013.description: Relates a work to an agent who is a director who is responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance.

P10014.label: has radio director agent
P10014.description: Relates a work to an agent who is a director who is responsible for the general management and supervision of a radio program.

P10015.label: has television director agent
P10015.description: Relates a work to an agent who is a director who is responsible for the general management and supervision of a television program.

P10016.label: is dramatized as work
P10016.description: Relates a work to a dramatic work that is adapted from another work.

P10017.label: has enacting jurisdiction
P10017.description: Relates a work to a corporate body who is a government enacting a work that is a law, regulation, constitution, court rule, or other legislation.

P10019.label: is part of work
P10019.description: Relates a work to a work that has another work as a discrete component.

P10020.label: has sequel work
P10020.description: Relates a work to a work that extends the narrative of another work forwards in time.

P10021.label: is replaced in part by work
P10021.description: Relates a work to a work whose content partially supersedes and renders obsolete the content of another work.

P10022.label: is replaced by work
P10022.description: Relates a work to a work whose content supersedes and renders obsolete the content of another work.

P10023.label: is adapted in verse as work
P10023.description: Relates a work to a literary composition in verse form adapted from a source work.

P10024.label: has coordinates of cartographic content
P10024.description: Relates a work to a place that is the area of coverage of a cartographic work that is described using a mathematical system to identify its boundaries or location.

P10025.label: is adapted as motion picture work
P10025.description: Relates a work to a motion picture work that is based on another work.

P10026.label: has cadenza work
P10026.description: Relates a work to a musical work that is an ornamental passage for a soloist added to a musical work, such as a concerto, by the same or a different composer.

P10027.label: is variations based on work
P10027.description: Relates a work to a musical work from which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material is taken to form a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.

P10028.label: is modified by variation as work
P10028.description: Relates a work to a musical work in which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material taken from another work forms a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.

P10029.label: is cadenza composed for work
P10029.description: Relates a work to a musical work, such as a concerto, to which is added a musical work that is an ornamental passage for a soloist by the same or a different composer.

P10030.label: is libretto for work
P10030.description: Relates a work to a work that is a musical or choreographic work such as an opera, a ballet, or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio, that is complemented by a textual work.

P10031.label: has incidental music work
P10031.description: Relates a work to a musical work that complements a work that is a play or other work for the stage that is realized as spoken word.

P10032.label: is remade as work
P10032.description: Relates a work to a motion picture, radio program, television program, or video that is based on an earlier work.

P10033.label: is set to music as work
P10033.description: Relates a work to a non-dramatic musical work, other than an oratorio, that uses the text of a source work.

P10034.label: is adapted as novel work
P10034.description: Relates a work to a novel adapted from a source work.

P10035.label: has appellee person
P10035.description: Relates a work to a person against whom an appeal is taken on a decision of a lower court recorded in a legal work of a higher court.

P10036.label: has medium
P10036.description: Relates a work to a person who claims to be a channel of communication with a world of spirits.

P10041.label: has degree supervisor
P10041.description: Relates a work to an academic supervisor who is responsible for advising or overseeing thesis or dissertation research for an academic degree that results in a work.

P10042.label: has appellant person
P10042.description: Relates a work to a person who appeals a decision of a lower court recorded in a legal work of a higher court.

P10043.label: has plaintiff person
P10043.description: Relates a work to a person who brings a suit in a civil proceeding.

P10044.label: has judge
P10044.description: Relates a work to a person who hears and decides on legal matters in court.

P10045.label: has praeses
P10045.description: Relates a work to a person who is a faculty moderator of an academic disputation, normally proposing a thesis and participating in the ensuing disputation.

P10046.label: has issuing body agent
P10046.description: Relates a work to an agent who issues a work.

P10047.label: has other agent associated with work (Deprecated)
P10047.description: Relates a work to an agent other than a creator associated with a work. (Deprecated)

P10048.label: has dedicator agent
P10048.description: Relates a work to an agent who assigns a work as an acknowledgement of the inspiration or support of a related agent.

P10049.label: has honouree agent of work
P10049.description: Relates a work to an agent who is honoured by a work.

P10050.label: has programmer agent
P10050.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for creating a computer program.

P10051.label: has designer agent
P10051.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for creating a design for an object.

P10052.label: has cartographer agent of work
P10052.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for a cartographic work.

P10053.label: has composer agent of work
P10053.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for creating a musical work.

P10054.label: has inventor agent
P10054.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for creating a new device or process.

P10055.label: has compiler agent
P10055.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for creating a new work such as a bibliography or a directory by selecting, arranging, aggregating, and editing data, information, etc.

P10056.label: has photographer agent of work
P10056.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for creating a photographic work.

P10057.label: has interviewer agent of work
P10057.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for creating a work by acting as an interviewer, reporter, pollster, or some other kind of agent who gathers information.

P10058.label: has artist agent
P10058.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for creating an original graphic design, drawing, painting, etc.

P10059.label: has interviewee agent of work
P10059.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for creating a work by responding to an interviewer, usually a reporter, pollster, or some other kind of agent who gathers information.

P10060.label: has choreographer agent
P10060.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for a choreographic work.

P10061.label: has author agent
P10061.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for a textual work.

P10062.label: has architect agent
P10062.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for an architectural design, including a pictorial representation intended to show how a building or other structure will look when completed.

P10063.label: has filmmaker agent
P10063.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for creating an independent or personal film.

P10064.label: has producer agent
P10064.description: Relates a work to an agent responsible for most of the business aspects of a production for screen, sound recording, television, webcast, etc.

P10065.label: has creator agent of work
P10065.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for a work.

P10066.label: has director agent
P10066.description: Relates a work to an agent who is responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance, a radio or television program, etc.

P10067.label: has sponsoring agent of work
P10067.description: Relates a work to an agent who sponsors some aspect of a work.

P10068.label: has director agent of photography
P10068.description: Relates a work to an agent who captures images, either electronically or on film or video stock, and often selects and arranges the lighting.

P10069.label: has dedicatee agent of work
P10069.description: Relates a work to an agent to whom a work is dedicated.

P10070.label: has addressee agent
P10070.description: Relates a work to an agent to whom a work or a portion of a work is addressed.

P10071.label: has consultant agent
P10071.description: Relates a work to an agent who provides consultation services, and often makes recommendations, for a related agent who is represented as a creator of a work.

P10072.label: has manifestation of work
P10072.description: Relates a work to a physical embodiment of a work.

P10073.label: has film producer agent
P10073.description: Relates a work to an agent who is a producer who is responsible for most of the business aspects of a film.

P10074.label: has radio producer agent
P10074.description: Relates a work to an agent who is a producer who is responsible for most of the business aspects of a radio program.

P10075.label: has television producer agent
P10075.description: Relates a work to an agent who is a producer who is responsible for most of the business aspects of a television program.

P10076.label: is adapted as radio program work
P10076.description: Relates a work to a radio program based on a source work.

P10077.label: has academic degree
P10077.description: Relates a work to a rank conferred as a guarantee of academic proficiency.

P10078.label: has expression of work
P10078.description: Relates a work to a realization of a work in the form of alpha-numeric, musical or choreographic notation, sound, image, object, movement, etc., or any combination of such forms.

P10079.label: has numeric designation of musical work
P10079.description: Relates a work to a serial number, opus number, or thematic index number assigned to a musical work by a composer, publisher, or musicologist.

P10080.label: has subseries
P10080.description: Relates a work to a work that is a successive aggregating work that is inspired by the overall editorial policy, scope, and style of another successive aggregating work.

P10081.label: has longitude and latitude
P10081.description: Relates a work to a place that is the area of coverage of a cartographic work that is identified using the longitude of the westernmost and easternmost boundaries and the latitude of the northernmost and southernmost boundaries.

P10082.label: has right ascension and declination
P10082.description: Relates a work to a place that that is the location of a celestial body that is the coverage of a cartographic work and is identified using the angles of right ascension and declination.

P10083.label: has strings of coordinate pairs
P10083.description: Relates a work to a place that is the area of coverage of a cartographic work that is identifiedy by a polygon using coordinates for each vertex.

P10084.label: has system of organization
P10084.description: Relates a work to a system of arranging materials in an archival resource or a collection.

P10085.label: is adapted as television program work
P10085.description: Relates a work to a television program based on a source work.

P10086.label: has variant title of work
P10086.description: Relates a work to a title of work that is not selected for preference in a specific application or context.

P10087.label: is adapted as video work
P10087.description: Relates a work to a video based on a source work.

P10088.label: has title of work
P10088.description: Relates a work to an appellation of work in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse.

P10089.label: is abstracted in work
P10089.description: Relates a work to a work that abstracts the contents of another work.

P10090.label: is indexed in work
P10090.description: Relates a work to a work that indexes the contents of a related work.

P10091.label: is adapted as choreography work
P10091.description: Relates a work to a choreographic work based on a related work.

P10092.label: has errata work
P10092.description: Relates a work to a work that consists of errors discovered after the publication of a predominant work, with their corrections.

P10093.label: has illustrations work
P10093.description: Relates a work to a work that consists of pictorial content designed to explain or decorate an augmented work.

P10094.label: is adapted as motion picture screenplay work
P10094.description: Relates a work to a work that consists of a screenplay for a motion picture, based on a source work.

P10098.label: is adapted as radio script work

P10099.label: is freely translated as work
P10099.description: Relates a work to a work that is both an adaptation and a translation into another language of a source work.

P10100.label: is description of work
P10100.description: Relates a work to a work that is described by a work.

P10101.label: is subseries of
P10101.description: Relates a work to a work that is a successive aggregating work that inspires the editorial policy, scope, and style of another successive aggregating work.

P10102.label: is issue of
P10102.description: Relates a work to a work that is a successive aggregating work that inspires the editorial policy, scope, and style of a static work.

P10103.label: is complemented by work
P10103.description: Relates a work to a work paired with a related work without either work being considered to be predominant.

P10105.description: Relates a work to a work that uses a screenplay that is complemented by a textual work.
